metadata.name: BLUE EYES
metadata.description:
This horse seemed magical to me when I saw it on the side of the road. I stopped immediately because I was so excited. I slipped, hit my head on the car door, which resulted in a huge bump on my forehead, grabbed my film camera and snapped this image. 
ThatÂ´s the story. 
The bump went away, the image stayed.

Nikon FM3A, on Kodak Gold 200


EDITION: 1/1
